---
// Top-of-leaf navigation: Back + Start over.
---

<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
  <button
    type="button"
    data-collab-back
    class="text-sm text-ink/70 hover:text-red-500 underline-offset-2 hover:underline"
  >
    ← Back
  </button>
  <span class="text-ink/30">/</span>
  <button
    type="button"
    data-collab-restart
    class="text-sm text-ink/70 hover:text-red-500 underline-offset-2 hover:underline"
  >
    Start over
  </button>
</div>
